item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: Joss1995
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:

Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)

...or something like this:

The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.

As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

item.title: Privacy Policy
item.dc:creator: Joss1995
item.content:encoded:
Who we are

Suggested text: Our website address is: http://nebula-2.local.

Comments

Suggested text: When visitors leave comments on the site we collect the data shown in the comments form, and also the visitor’s IP address and browser user agent string to help spam detection.

An anonymized string created from your email address (also called a hash) may be provided to the Gravatar service to see if you are using it. The Gravatar service privacy policy is available here: https://automattic.com/privacy/. After approval of your comment, your profile picture is visible to the public in the context of your comment.

Media

Suggested text: If you upload images to the website, you should avoid uploading images with embedded location data (EXIF GPS) included. Visitors to the website can download and extract any location data from images on the website.

Cookies

Suggested text: If you leave a comment on our site you may opt-in to saving your name, email address and website in cookies. These are for your convenience so that you do not have to fill in your details again when you leave another comment. These cookies will last for one year.

If you visit our login page, we will set a temporary cookie to determine if your browser accepts cookies. This cookie contains no personal data and is discarded when you close your browser.

When you log in, we will also set up several cookies to save your login information and your screen display choices. Login cookies last for two days, and screen options cookies last for a year. If you select "Remember Me", your login will persist for two weeks. If you log out of your account, the login cookies will be removed.

If you edit or publish an article, an additional cookie will be saved in your browser. This cookie includes no personal data and simply indicates the post ID of the article you just edited. It expires after 1 day.

Embedded content from other websites

Suggested text: Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images, articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if the visitor has visited the other website.

These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party tracking, and monitor your interaction with that embedded content, including tracking your interaction with the embedded content if you have an account and are logged in to that website.

Who we share your data with

Suggested text: If you request a password reset, your IP address will be included in the reset email.

How long we retain your data

Suggested text: If you leave a comment, the comment and its metadata are retained indefinitely. This is so we can recognize and approve any follow-up comments automatically instead of holding them in a moderation queue.

For users that register on our website (if any), we also store the personal information they provide in their user profile. All users can see, edit, or delete their personal information at any time (except they cannot change their username). Website administrators can also see and edit that information.

What rights you have over your data

Suggested text: If you have an account on this site, or have left comments, you can request to receive an exported file of the personal data we hold about you, including any data you have provided to us. You can also request that we erase any personal data we hold about you. This does not include any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.

Where your data is sent

Suggested text: Visitor comments may be checked through an automated spam detection service.

About

We Serve Tasty Grilled Goodness!

Nebula es un restobar único que combina una atmósfera cósmica con una experiencia culinaria excepcional. Con una decoración inspirada en el universo y una variedad de platos creativos, desde delicias a la parrilla hasta opciones vegetarianas, Nebula te invita a explorar nuevos sabores mientras te sumerges en un ambiente celestial.

Sobre Nosotros

nuestro equipo está compuesto por apasionados profesionales de la gastronomía que comparten un compromiso inquebrantable con la excelencia y la creatividad.

History

Establecido en 2003

"Nebula", un restobar establecido en 2003, ha sido un punto de referencia en la escena gastronómica desde su creación. Ubicado en el centro del universo, este lugar combina una atmósfera acogedora con una cocina innovadora y una excelente selección de bebidas. Desde sus inicios, Nebula se ha destacado por su atención al detalle, ofreciendo platos creativos y una experiencia culinaria única para sus clientes. Nebula se ha convertido en un destino popular tanto para locales como para visitantes, consolidándose como un lugar emblemático en la escena gastronómica de la ciudad. Su legado de más de dos décadas es testimonio de su dedicación a proporcionar momentos memorables a todos los que cruzan sus puertas..

As Seen On

Experimenta una cena inolvidable en el restaurante Nebula.

Sumérgete en una experiencia culinaria incomparable en Nebula, donde la magia de la gastronomía se fusiona con un ambiente celestial para crear momentos memorables..

Berenjena eso

Berenjena rellena de quinoa, verduras y nueces, gratinada y cubierta de galaxia cremosa de zapallo con queso vegano

S/. 35
Galaxia de Legumbres

Guiso de lentejas, garbanzos y frijoles negros en una salsa de tomate y especias, servido con quinoa.

S/. 45
Estrella de Pollo al Curry

Pechuga de pollo en una salsa de curry cremosa con leche de coco, acompañado de arroz basmati.

S/. 55
Potaje Arcoíris

Un potaje vibrante y nutritivo que evoca las coloridas nebulosas del cosmos. Hecho con una variedad de vegetales frescos como zanahorias, remolachas, pimientos, espinacas y calabaza.

$15
Vórtice de Tofu

Tofu marinado en salsa de soja y jengibre, salteado con vegetales frescos y mezclado con arroz jazmín.

S/. 48
Supernova de Lomo Fino

Lomo Fino a la parrilla servido con risotto de loche, camote y papas fritas, con cremoso sorpresa.

S/. 75
Sopa Nebulosa Verde

Una sopa verde vibrante inspirada en la belleza de las nebulosas, hecha con una base de espinacas, guisantes y albahaca, logrando un color esmeralda leve.

S/. 45

Desserts

Torta Estelar

Una tarta cósmica de vainilla en capas, teñida con tonos azules, morados y negros, imitando las nebulosas del espacio, rellena de crema de mascarpone y arándanos.

S/. 120
Constelación de Cheesecake

Cheesecake de vainilla con remolinos de salsa de frutos rojos, decorado con estrellas de chocolate blanco.

S/. 25
Alfajores Cometa

Los alfajores son deliciosos dulces tradicionales de América Latina. Se componen de dos suaves galletas de maicena que se deshacen en la boca, unidas por una capa generosa de dulce de leche.

S/. 85 - 12 docena S/. 10 - Unidad
Açai Constelación

Açai bowl con fruta servida en una constelación de yogurt y nueces espaciales.

S/. 22

Appetizers

Lunar verde de Salmón Ahumado

Salmón ahumado, acompañado de crema de queso, servido encima de un esponjosos de albahaca.

S/. 28
Estrellas de Queso de Cabra

tartitas de queso de cabra con hierbas y pistachos, servidas con galletas saladas.

S/. 26
Tiradito Cósmico

Un tiradito que captura la esencia del cosmos, con finas láminas de pescado fresco marinadas en una vibrante leche de tigre morada y amarilla.

S/. 55
Nebulosa de Coliflor

Puré de coliflor con cúrcuma y especias, servida con una salsa de tahini de remolacha que le da un color vibrante.

S/. 29

Beverages

Burbujas Supernova

Mezcla de bourbon, jugo de naranja, jarabe de granadina, y un toque de amargo de angostura, creando un efecto de eclipse en el vaso.

S/. 22
Vía Láctea Dulce

Mezcla de vodka, crema de cacao, crema irlandesa, y un toque de leche condensada, servido con hielo.

S/. 20
Nebulosa Cósmica

Un cóctel vibrante con base de vodka, licor de arándano, jugo de lima, y un toque de brillo comestible para darle un efecto cósmico.

S/. 25
Bruma Galáctica

Mezcla de ginebra, licor de flor de saúco, jugo de toronja, y un dash de agua tónica para una apariencia nebulosa.

S/. 20
Vórtice Celestial

Mezcla de whisky, licor de manzana verde, jugo de lima, y soda de jengibre, creando un vórtice de sabores.

S/. 25
